WEBVTT

00:03.062 --> 00:06.314
AFFAIRS OF THE HEART

00:06.481 --> 00:08.566
Excuse me, cutie.

00:10.317 --> 00:13.736
Cutie?
Who do you think you're talking to?

00:14.821 --> 00:17.823
- Her.
- Better be.

00:17.989 --> 00:21.909
- As long as you're here.
- I ain't here.

00:22.076 --> 00:27.789
What's the matter? Did we get up on the
the wrong side of the web this morning?

00:28.872 --> 00:33.126
- I hate it when they call me cutie.
- I know how you feeI.

00:33.292 --> 00:37.546
Earlier, a customer had the effrontery
to refer to me as "honey".

00:37.712 --> 00:41.173
But that makes sense.
Honey is bee barf.

00:48.011 --> 00:52.306
- Did that snort mean we were amused?
- No, definitely not.

00:52.473 --> 00:55.268
That was a snort of disapprovaI.

